name: Kylin Network
public_notice: Kylin Network (KYL) has recently migrated from their old contract to a new one. For more information, please visit this Medium post.

description.en: Kylin Network offers any applications and blockchains (such as parachains and parathreads) instantaneous but reliable and valid on/off-chain market data and social data sources by leveraging the power of Polkadot/Substrate Framework on open networks.
